data.title: Newsweek Ranks Delgado among Top Online Colleges in America
data.text:
Newsweek magazine’s annual rankings of the Top Online Colleges in America have been released for 2023. Delgado Community College is at Number 126 on the publication’s list of 200 outstanding online colleges and universities.

In Louisiana, only LSU appears with Delgado on the list of Top Online Colleges in America. The state’s flagship university’s LSU Online division is ranked at number 64.
